zine 容易入口啲呢點部分同意 不過我麻麻地TIME既style <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我覺得佢好處有 <br />\n1) 各國時事/Global affairs(美歐中亞, 拉丁美洲同非洲都有) 有無用一回事 不過中學生見識多啲係好嘅  不過咁 始終係時事雜誌 本野就一定有自己既立場同傾向既, 想深入了解多啲 睇死一本係唔夠 (不過for英文就駛但啦)<br />\n<br />\n2) 除咗時事之外佢有 Technology, Literature section講相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n3) 了解下點樣present 啲argument 同埋字裡行間會有少少humor 既tone可以留意下<br />\n<br />\n4) 起碼係English speaker寫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你睇一次中國/香港non English speaker人寫文同 Native寫個style係有啲分別  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或者個人對時事無咩興趣 (雖然我強烈建議任何人了解多啲時事) 可以睇下自己中意睇咩再決定  Scientific American, National Geographic, Forbes, Bloomberg... etc.<br />\n<br />\nPS  少少雞蛋裡挑骨頭 本野其實係 &ldquo;The&rdquo; Economist <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3c1cfed3c8e61898864ca449d08498f7a07a58","tid":771843,"uid":126675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T18:27:26.000Z","msg":"咁算 此post 已完"},{"pid":"e7859c3d087075b006b34e68ac9a5b8aa6ae8e5a","tid":771843,"uid":126675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f274a501753227cd4deb480fc37b49edb9970686","tid":771843,"uid":57148,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"035ee02dfd9d7945004d428e2cef6b70504ac684","tid":771843,"uid":133896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4802be4eb86c01bc852fbf3e13ff265b62640481","tid":771843,"uid":57148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:28:42.000Z","msg":"上佢官網 / 書展有幾間係專搞雜誌訂閱 / 呢啲公司有時會係U擺counter (唔肯定係咪間間都係,  但係我嗰間係)<br />\n<br />\n當然上佢官網最方便 同埋唔駛俾班sales sell到你煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你自問平時唔點睇書既話訂digital就夠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"我想改善DSE 英文作文, economist推介嗎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T18:04:53.000Z","msg":"The Economist 行文同用